Available Tools: get_lab_results | get_latest_results | get_result_history | download_report
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "patient_id": "string", "test_type": "string", "from_date": "string" }
Response Schema: { "results": [{ "test": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "reference_range": "string", "status": "normal|high|low" }] }
---
Question: Retrieve the most recent iron panel data for patient P-3344.
Call: { "func_call": "get_latest_results", "patient_id": "P-3344", "test_type": "iron_panel", "from_date": "" }
Response: { "results": [{ "test": "Serum Iron", "value": 55, "unit": "mcg/dL", "reference_range": "60-170", "status": "low" }, { "test": "Ferritin", "value": 12, "unit": "ng/mL", "reference_range": "12-150", "status": "normal" }, { "test": "TIBC", "value": 420, "unit": "mcg/dL", "reference_range": "240-450", "status": "normal" }] }

